title:
['Shiva Devalaya (no. 5) – ශිව දේවාලය (අංක 5)']

Rating:
['2', '4.50']

Content:

This large devalaya, a place of worship for Hindus and Buddhists has been partially restored and has two main devalas for god Vishnu and god Shiva. Inside the devala you will see a Virgina and a “
” (penis of god Shiva) , both items of worship can bee seen.





